<p><b>What is the summary of novel pursuit of happiness?</b> The Pursuit of Happyness is a book that tells the inspiring story of Chris Gardner, a man who overcame poverty and homelessness to become a successful stockbroker. The book is a memoir that chronicles Gardner's struggles and triumphs, and it is a testament to the power of perseverance and self-belief.</p>
